                        <span>介绍：普通的土地，只能种出最普通的作物。</span>
                        <span>产出：苹果、萝卜。</span>
                    </div>
                </dd>

                <dd class="clear">
                    <div class="img">
                        <img src="/Content/images/22.png">
                    </div>
                    <div class="txt">
                        <span>名称：<b>红土地</b></span>
                        <span>介绍：改良过的土地，可以种植4种不同的作物。</span>
                        <span>产出：苹果、萝卜、辣椒、西瓜</span>
                    </div>
                </dd>

                <dd class="clear">
                    <div class="img">
                        <img src="/Content/images/33.png">
                    </div>
                    <div class="txt">
                        <span>名称：<b>黑土地</b></span>
